  "body": "### Version of Hardhat\n\n2.12.7\n\n### What happened?\n\nI was trying to deploy hardhat.\r\nAfter adding hardhat dependencies . \r\nWhen I went to yarn hardhat run scripts/deploy.js\r\n\n\n### Minimal reproduction steps\n\n```solidity\r\nyarn hardhat run scripts/deploy.js\r\nyarn run v1.22.15\r\nwarning ../../package.json: No license field\r\n$ /home/nakesh/folder/hardhat-simple-storage-fcc/node_modules/.bin/hardhat run scripts/deploy.js\r\nError HH801: Plugin @nomicfoundation/hardhat-chai-matchers requires the following dependencies to be installed: ethers.\r\nPlease run: npm install --save-dev \"ethers@^5.0.0\"\r\n\r\nFor more info go to https://hardhat.org/HH801 or run Hardhat with --show-stack-traces\r\nerror Command failed with exit code 1.\r\ninfo Visit https://yarnpkg.com/en/docs/cli/run for documentation about this command.\r\n```\n\n### Search terms\n\n_No response_",
